; @tremor/react still pins React 18 in its peer ranges as of v3.18.x, but
; the rest of the project has been on React 19 since the upgrade. Honour
; the peer warning instead of failing — both upstreams (Tremor and the
; React 19 deps it complains about) work fine in practice. Revisit when
; @tremor/react ships a React-19-clean version.
legacy-peer-deps=true
